PI-TOPSoftware招聘
急招-嵌入式硬件工程师
15k-22k /深圳 / 经验5-10年 / 本科及以上 / 全职
硬件制造
嵌入式
2天前  发布于拉勾网职位诱惑：
周末双休,弹性工作制,高薪,年轻的团队
职位描述：
******有意者请投英文或中英文简历********
Position: Embedded Hardware Engineer

Responsibilities:
1 Selecting appropriate MCU for a wide range of projects and applications. 为广泛的项目和应用选择合适的MCU。
Writing and maintaining software for microcontrollers, usually in C/C++.
熟悉用C / C ++编写和维护微控制器的软件
2 Software: architecture definition, coding, testing, debugging, and documentation
软件方面：体系结构定义，编码，测试，调试和文档工作
3 Hardware: Low-level PCB design, schematic capture, component selection, troubleshooting. Being familiar with the layout process is also a bonus, but not a requirement.硬件方面：低级PCB设计，原理图捕捉，组件选择，故障排除。熟悉布局过程优先考虑，但不是硬性要求。
4 Collaborate with other team members (including both hardware and software engineers) to agree system designs, interfaces and protocols etc.与其他团队成员（包括硬件和软件工程师）协商系统设计，接口和协议等并达成一致目标。
5 Flexibility is essential - specifications may not be fully defined at the start of development, and liaison with rest of team for continued feedback and input of requirements is likely throughout the development.具备灵活性是刚性要求 - 具体规范可能在一开始并不会完全定义完整，同时你需要与其他团队保持联系和意见输入，以便在整个开发过程中获得持续的反馈意见。
6 Write detailed technical documentation, where required, for UK-based team members (esp. software team) to understand how they can ‘talk to’ the embedded firmware.根据需要，为英国团队成员（尤其是软件团队）撰写详细的技术文档，以了解他们如何与嵌入式固件“沟通”。

Requirements:
Essential:
1 Degree qualified in Electronic Engineering or related subject电子工程或相关专业学历
2 Minimum of 5 years proven experience in industry 至少5年的行业经验
3 Deeply familiar with a range of microcontrollers, especially STM32, PIC and AVR chipsets, and their respective strengths and weaknesses (e.g. speed, flash size, peripherals etc. versus price and availability).深入了解各种微控制器，尤其是STM32，PIC和AVR芯片组及其各自的优缺点（例如速度，闪存大小，外设等与价格和可用性等）。
4 C/C++ expert, extremely experienced in writing perfect, clean, reliable, thoroughly bug-free code for embedded systems, with extensive experience in thoroughly testing all code to ensure reliability.  精通C / C ++，擅长为嵌入式系统编写完美，干净，可靠，彻底的无误的代码，在全面测试所有代码以确保可靠性方面拥有丰富的经验。
5 Very comfortable working with I2C, SPI, UART, USB, I2S and other chip-to-chip protocols.熟练使用I2C，SPI，UART，USB，I2S和其他芯片到芯片协议
6 Able to design schematics, especially those involving microcontrollers, and proficient in the use of professional schematic capture software e.g. ORCAD, ALTIUM etc. 能够设计示意图，特别是涉及微控制器的示意图，并精通使用专业示意图捕捉软件，例如ORCAD，ALTIUM等
7 Fluent in written and spoken English, especially on technical subjects. Must be able to write comprehensive technical design documentation and reports in English and Chinese.流利的英文书写和口语技能，特别是技术项目上。必须能够用英文和中文编写全面的技术设计文件和报告。

Desirable:
1 Experience in PIC, MSP430 and other popular microcontrollers. PIC，MSP430和其他流行的微控制器的相关工作经验。
2 Familiar with PCB layout and good layout techniques.熟悉PCB布局和良好的布局技术。
3 Experience working with Cadence ORCAD/ALLEGRO schematic/layout software.使用Cadence ORCAD / ALLEGRO原理图/布局软件的相关工作经验。

******加入我们，你将享受*********
社保和住房公积金；
五天工作制；
公司年轻的团队有非常融洽的工作氛围；
 享受国家法定的节假日；不定期团建活动；
 每年公司安排体检；
 工作满一年13薪待遇。
